    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-09-24T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-09-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="330"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d330">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Baker</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-09-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 24, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Nicaraguan minister says Wiltbank and Lampton will be allowed, on request, to
                    return to Bluefields to wind up business. Have they property or families at
                    Bluefields or in Mosquito? In what business were they before July 5? Communicate
                    with them without delay and report.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
